            "url": "http://example.com/2023/07/13/github-image-hosting-service/",
            "title": "使用 Github + PicGo 搭建图床",
            "date_published": "2023-07-13T11:52:15.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"使用-github-picgo-搭建图床\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#使用-github-picgo-搭建图床\">#</a> 使用 Github + PicGo 搭建图床</h2>\n<p>参考教程：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly96aHVhbmxhbi56aGlodS5jb20vcC80ODkyMzY3Njk=\">使用 Github+picGo 搭建图床，保姆级教程来了 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"创建仓库\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#创建仓库\">#</a> 创建仓库</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>在 Github 创建一个仓库，用于存放图片资源</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在 Github 设置中生成 Token</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>下载 PicGo，<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL01vbHVuZXJmaW5uL1BpY0dvL3JlbGVhc2Vz\">Releases · Molunerfinn/PicGo (github.com)</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在 PicGo 设置图床</p>\n<img data-src=\"/2023/07/13/github-image-hosting-service/image-20230713200058971.png\" class=\"\" title=\"PicGo配置Github图床\">\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"测试\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#测试\">#</a> 测试</h3>\n<p>在 PicGo 上传图片，上传成功后 Github 仓库应有上传的图片，复制图片链接到浏览器应能访问图片。</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Github",
                "PicGo"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://example.com/2023/07/13/hexo-guide/",
            "url": "http://example.com/2023/07/13/hexo-guide/",
            "title": "Hexo 的基本使用",
            "date_published": "2023-07-13T11:33:45.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"hexo-的基本使用\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#hexo-的基本使用\">#</a> Hexo 的基本使用</h2>\n<h3 id=\"创建文章\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#创建文章\">#</a> 创建文章</h3>\n<p>修改 <code>_config.yml文件</code> ，生成文章的同时，生成一个同名的资源目录，这样在引用图片时，可以使用相对路径引用。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">post_asset_folder: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>创建一个名为 <code>hexo-guide</code>  的文章</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new post hexo-guide</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Front-matter 是文件最上方以  <code>---</code>  分隔的区域，用于指定个别文件的变量，举例来说：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: Hello World</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: 2013/7/13 20:46:25</span><br><span class=\"line\">tag: [&#x27;test&#x27;] # 文章标签</span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>文章的 Markdown 文件里，通过以下方式即可引用对应的图片。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% asset_img [路径] [图片题注] %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"创建关于页\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#创建关于页\">#</a> 创建「关于页」</h3>\n<p>使用以下命令创建一个关于页面</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new page about</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>创建成功后修改  <code>/source/about/index.md</code> ，添加 layout 属性。修改后的文件示例如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">---title: 标题layout: about---这里写关于页的正文，支持 Markdown, HTML</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Hexo"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://example.com/2023/07/11/my-blog-build-remark/",
            "url": "http://example.com/2023/07/11/my-blog-build-remark/",
            "title": "基于 GitHub Pages + Hexo 搭建个人博客",
            "date_published": "2023-07-11T15:05:51.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"基于hexogithubpages搭建个人博客\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#基于hexogithubpages搭建个人博客\">#</a> 基于 Hexo+GitHubPages 搭建个人博客</h2>\n<p>参考教程：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly94aWUuaW5mb3EuY24vYXJ0aWNsZS9hYzUxY2UxZjZlOTQzNDc3OWMzNWNiYjZj\">白嫖 GitHub Pages，轻松搭建个人博客_Hexo_LigaAI_InfoQ 写作社区</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"github-pages-是什么\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#github-pages-是什么\">#</a> GitHub Pages 是什么？</h3>\n<p>GitHub Pages 是由 GitHub 官方提供的一种免费的静态站点托管服务，让我们可以在 GitHub 仓库里托管和发布自己的静态网站页面。</p>\n<h3 id=\"hexo-是什么\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#hexo-是什么\">#</a> Hexo 是什么？</h3>\n<p>Hexo 是一个快速、简洁且高效的静态博客框架，它基于 Node.js 运行，可以将我们撰写的 Markdown 文档解析渲染成静态的 HTML 网页。</p>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3poLWNuL2RvY3Mv\">文档 | Hexo</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"原理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#原理\">#</a> 原理</h3>\n<p>在本地撰写 Markdown 格式文章后，通过 Hexo 解析文档，渲染生成具有主题样式的 HTML 静态网页，再推送到 GitHub 上完成博文的发布。</p>\n<h3 id=\"步骤\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#步骤\">#</a> 步骤</h3>\n<p>开始前需确认已安装 Git 和 NodeJS，且能使用 npm 工具。</p>\n<h4 id=\"配置github-pages\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#配置github-pages\">#</a> 配置 GitHub Pages</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>在 Github 上创建仓库，仓库名必须使用  <code>&lt;GitHub用户名&gt;.github.io</code>  格式。</li>\n<li>在仓库创建一个名为 <code>index.html</code>  的文件。</li>\n<li>访问 <code>https://&lt;GitHub 用户名&gt;.github.io</code> ，如果能访问成功，即代表 GitHub Pages 搭建成功。</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"安装hexo\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#安装hexo\">#</a> 安装 Hexo</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>全局安装 <code>hexo-cli</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>创建并初始化 hexo 项目</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n   <figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init my-blog</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd my-blog</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p>生成页面 &amp; 本地启动</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g &amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>本地访问</p>\n<p>浏览器访问：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cDovL2xvY2FsaG9zdDo0MDAwLw==\">http://localhost:4000/</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"配置主题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#配置主题\">#</a> 配置主题</h4>\n<p>Hexo 主题：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL3RoZW1lcy8=\">Themes | Hexo</span></p>\n<p>通常主题的 Github 仓库有文档介绍如何配置主题。</p>\n<h4 id=\"发布github-pages\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#发布github-pages\">#</a> 发布 GitHub Pages</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>安装 <code>hexo-deployer-git</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改 <code>config.yml</code> ，将以下信息替换</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: &lt;repository url&gt; # https://github.com/&lt;GitHub用户名&gt;/&lt;GitHub用户名&gt;.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: [branch] #分支名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">  token: [token]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>生成页面并推送至 Github 仓库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean &amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Hexo",
                "GitHub Pages"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://example.com/2023/07/11/hello-world/",
            "url": "http://example.com/2023/07/11/hello-world/",
            "title": "Hello World",
            "date_published": "2023-07-11T14:39:19.715Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Welcome to <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvLw==\">Hexo</span>! This is your very first post. Check <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mv\">documentation</span> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3MvdHJvdWJsZXNob290aW5nLmh0bWw=\">troubleshooting</span> or you can ask me on <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2hleG9qcy9oZXhvL2lzc3Vlcw==\">GitHub</span>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"quick-start\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#quick-start\">#</a> Quick Start</h2>\n<h3 id=\"create-a-new-post\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#create-a-new-post\">#</a> Create a new post</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvd3JpdGluZy5odG1s\">Writing</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"run-server\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#run-server\">#</a> Run server</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvc2VydmVyLmh0bWw=\">Server</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"generate-static-files\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#generate-static-files\">#</a> Generate static files</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3MvZ2VuZXJhdGluZy5odG1s\">Generating</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites\">#</a> Deploy to remote sites</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvb25lLWNvbW1hbmQtZGVwbG95bWVudC5odG1s\">Deployment</span></p>\n",
            "tags": []
        }
    ]
